Attribution Notice:

This project is based on:

- [Open5GS](https://open5gs.org) – an open-source 5G core network project.
- [docker_open5gs](https://github.com/herlesupreeth/docker_open5gs) by Supreeth Herle.

The repository includes substantial extensions and modifications by Neruzz to support:

- Dual SMF/UPF deployment across edge and cloud.
- APN-based user-plane selection.
- Two slices deployments
- Amarisoft gNB integration.
- Edge metrics Prometheus and Grafana.
- MQTT broker

**If you use or build upon this work, please provide appropriate credit to both original and extended authors.**
